title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data in a table, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: Expected Behavior: The data should be successfully exported.
SR: Steps to Reproduce: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Attempt to export data from a table containing highlight/map. 3. Observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
